Name: Source Notes
Total Population by Race/Ethnicity: U.S. Census Bureau, American Community Survey 5-Year Estimates, Table B03002 (2009-2018); retrieved https://data.census.gov/.

Name: Notes
Total Population by Race/Ethnicity: Percents refer to the percent of the total population. Racial/ethnic groups are defined as follows: White = non-Latino White alone, Black = non-Latino Black alone, Asian = non-Latino Asian or Pacific Islander alone, Other = other non-Latino of any race, Latino = Latino of any race.
